{"tid":1079212,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"秀智解約JYP？JYP放走了孝琳、樸草娥，IU的離去更是讓樸振英心痛","createTime":"2019-03-26T19:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T01:02:08.000Z","uid":34643,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f5330567fd946c48e0fe11a1279e4ab5ce09fa2d","tid":1079212,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T19:32:48.000Z","msg":"據韓媒報道：裴秀智和JYP娛樂公司的合同到期將不會續約，改簽經紀公司後的秀智將以SOOP所屬藝人身份進行演藝活動。<br />\n<br />\nJYP官方也表示，感謝秀智在過去9年的努力，以後也將會為秀智應援。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics4.baidu.com/feed/9213b07eca8065389df67852cc5e3240ac3482df.jpeg?token=9cb1148fbdc1f62f68d855f5efd7da0f&amp;s=15B8EC333EA8468C3E0045D0030030E2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics4.baidu.com%2Ffeed%2F9213b07eca8065389df67852cc5e3240ac3482df.jpeg%3Ftoken%3D9cb1148fbdc1f62f68d855f5efd7da0f%26s%3D15B8EC333EA8468C3E0045D0030030E2&h=1cff3349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裴秀智解約JYP<br />\n<br />\n裴秀智出道的Miss A組合已經於17年解散，當時組合還有兩位中國成員。<br />\n<br />\nMiss A的解散雖然蠻可惜的，但與其一直不溫不火，這樣反而感覺是個更好的結果了吧（不得不吐槽當時JYP公司資源傾斜秀智太多才是解散的矛盾誘因）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics3.baidu.com/feed/b3b7d0a20cf431ad1224dd8810b53fab2fdd9811.jpeg?token=859c86de46da6801e305594dcd41edcc&amp;s=FF3C34C780434BFDB229152B03003048\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics3.baidu.com%2Ffeed%2Fb3b7d0a20cf431ad1224dd8810b53fab2fdd9811.jpeg%3Ftoken%3D859c86de46da6801e305594dcd41edcc%26s%3DFF3C34C780434BFDB229152B03003048&h=ddf18136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裴秀智＆樸振英<br />\n<br />\n在此也是希望秀智後面的演藝事業一帆風順，繼續走花路吧~<br />\n<br />\n其實這些年JYP因&ldquo;慧眼&rdquo;不識珠而放走的明星不在少數，尤其是在練習生期間的好苗子。<br />\n<br />\n像EXO的金珉錫、EXID女團的HaNi、AOA王牌天使的樸草娥等等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics3.baidu.com/feed/35a85edf8db1cb130f8d628686d7c54a90584bc2.jpeg?token=ff70cc16da11bc967dfa46361be24485&amp;s=AEF27785025211D60830391F0300C0C0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics3.baidu.com%2Ffeed%2F35a85edf8db1cb130f8d628686d7c54a90584bc2.jpeg%3Ftoken%3Dff70cc16da11bc967dfa46361be24485%26s%3DAEF27785025211D60830391F0300C0C0&h=357d5d25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nEXID-Hani<br />\n<br />\n而下面這兩位從JPY走出的藝人絕對是能讓樸振英悔得腸子都青的那種：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n那麼這裡面有沒有您喜歡的明星呢？歡迎留言討論哦~<br />\n<br />\n喜歡的朋友別忘了點個贊再走，小編在此拜謝了！"},{"pid":"cb6726a29c85873ded3c575a6e5cd08b84add4d5","tid":1079212,"uid":7149,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T19:33:35.000Z","msg":"Iu bb"},{"pid":"962de78766f091ec56392fe64b5d9567106f5974","tid":1079212,"uid":34643,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb6726a29c85873ded3c575a6e5cd08b84add4d5","tid":1079212,"uid":7149,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T19:33:35.000Z","msg":"Iu bb"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T20:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://file2.instiz.net/data/cached_img/upload/2015070420/591e0c2f9c0cf37d26823f2631b0e087.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffile2.instiz.net%2Fdata%2Fcached_img%2Fupload%2F2015070420%2F591e0c2f9c0cf37d26823f2631b0e087.jpg&h=69b3d209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://file2.instiz.net/data/cached_img/upload/2015070421/824fffe6386ba9a09f46f9a7a8dfe997.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffile2.instiz.net%2Fdata%2Fcached_img%2Fupload%2F2015070421%2F824fffe6386ba9a09f46f9a7a8dfe997.jpg&h=7b78e81e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0525195a526a30985355efba30822cbd524f9bdc","tid":1079212,"uid":18587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T20:13:18.000Z","msg":"演藝界雲爺爺？"},{"pid":"af341dd1650fdbf0fd831cc86bce63032c3f8cc1","tid":1079212,"uid":56751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T21:30:31.000Z","msg":"拒絕IU係咩心態？？？"},{"pid":"54ce2a77eb2b50a2e6b4ec751b6a42ab11c07d42","tid":1079212,"uid":24329